ygData.messageBody:
I just looked this up last night since I have to do the quest a second time
<sigh>

Toris Ton - Emerald Jungle
Veksar Gron - Ill Omen
Ik Gron - City of Mist

The ones you don't have
Kaesora - Terraz Ton
Dalinir - Royal Crown of Dalnir (Not to be confused with Hair Grease...)
The Overther - Danark Gran

Slyde
